#: C/system-admin-guide.xml:4(para)
msgid "This chapter describes how to configure fonts in the MATE Desktop."
msgstr ""
"Ce chapitre explique comment configurer les polices dans le bureau MATE."

#: C/system-admin-guide.xml:8(title)
msgid "Introduction to Configuring Fonts"
